{"tid":1570024,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人權政策法案通過左!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-15T00:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:56:06.000Z","uid":51920,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd0b7914423ce8357cb09ccfec66519588288a9","tid":1570024,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:48:54.000Z","msg":"美參院通過《維吾爾人權政策法案》 中國外交部：停止干涉內政<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦參議院11日間一致通過《維吾爾人權政策法案》（Uighur Human Rights Policy Act），要求美國政府密切注意關押新疆維吾爾人的「再教育營」，並擬對負責再教育營政策的官員予以制裁。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國外交部12日表示，中方對此堅決反對，敦促美方停止借涉疆問題干涉中國內政，停止推動有關議案成法，以免損害中美關係大局。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9816df2deb94e30d42ef32e9c2e25355047b534b","tid":1570024,"uid":187355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:51:03.000Z","msg":"過左好耐啦屌你老尾"},{"pid":"e46e911e6c1ea67dc0051c84a5faa18d8e98b910","tid":1570024,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5a45a06e27299020b2254c5879418f800405af","tid":1570024,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"告咗steam先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833d02bf42362e7259ceb91ff1454cfc4e0a2a18","tid":1570024,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac5a45a06e27299020b2254c5879418f800405af","tid":1570024,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"告咗steam先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}